<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.4.7">
<l>vāmaṉaṉ kaṟki matucūtaṉ mātavaṉ</l>
<l>tārmaṉṉu tācarati yāya taṭamārvaṉ</l>
<l>kāmaṉṟaṉ tātaikaṇ ṇapurat temperumāṉ</l>
<l>tāma naṟuntuḻāy tāḻntūtāy kōltumpī.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Twiggy dragonfly, alight and sip the fragrant tulasī in the wreath</l>
<l>Of Vāmana, Kalki, Madhusūdana, Mādhava,</l>
<l>The one with a broad chest where a garland was fixed</l>
<l rend="indent">when he became Dāsarathi,</l>
<l>Grandfather to Kāma, our lord of Kaṇṇapuram.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
